room_title: Escape room "The Millionaire Murder Escape" by Times Up! Escape Rooms in Raleigh - Durham
review: The atmosphere inside the rooms are amazing. I did the millionaire room, it was challenging and fun. We didn't get out but I would recommend this escape room!

room_title: Escape room "The Millionaire Murder Escape" by Times Up! Escape Rooms in Raleigh - Durham
review: I have done the Millionaire Murder escape at Time's Up. The clues were challenging and there were some unexpected surprises in the room that made the experience super fun. The staff was professional and friendly. I would definitely recommend this room for a big group. It was a blast!

room_title: Escape room "The Millionaire Murder Escape" by Times Up! Escape Rooms in Raleigh - Durham
review: We did the millionaire murder escape. We had 7 people in our group. We did a damn good job as a team! We had some funny moments. If we had 15 more mins we would have gotten out. We are definitely going back to try the other rooms.
